name: Marla Janak
description: I am a licensed real estate agent with Berkshire Hathaway Home Services/Ambassador Real Estate. I have spent my life as an educator in the public schools and now specialize in coaching new home buyers and sellers as a realtor. I develop a strong trustworthy relationship with my clients by guiding them through one the of the most important financial decisions they will make in their lifetime. I have developed my communication skills by working with thousands of young musicians as an instrumental band director in the public schools for 30+ years. I also perform on stage as a professional trumpet player with many excellent performing groups and top-notch musicians.
